newly minted police partners risking their own 
lives to determine whether a fellow officer was 
murdered in this gritty crime drama set in New

chaos of the storm -- one of the most violent 
natural disasters the nation's ever seen -- but 
the evidence doesn't seem to add up. Sharon Stone 
co-stars.
